title: OF- Brand new 3 bed, 3 bath luxury  w/rooftop
posting_body: ['100 S Orlando', 'Los Angeles, CA 90048', 'PICTURES SHOWN ARE STOCK PHOTOS AND NOT OF THE ACTUAL UNIT', 'Brand new luxury Apartments Parking Included.', 'Welcome home, a brand new construction offering the best in West Hollywood living.', 'In addition to bright, modern interiors, this 3 bedroom boasts designer fixtures, in unit washer and dryer, walk-in closets, and luxury appliances.', 'Moments away from high-end dining and nightlife on Santa Monica Blvd.', "Whether you're looking for city luxuries or a natural getaway, offers it all.", 'is the perfect place to experience good living as friendly and professional leasing, management and maintenance teams cater to your needs.', 'Highlights: -In unit washer/dryer -Stainless steel appliances -All units come with 2 (two) tandem parking spaces only Pets accepted with additional pet rent.', 'For more information or for an appointment, please contact our building manager Josh via text at', 'show contact info', '.']
